    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a mechanism using which a DNS client
      can receive information about the freshness of a zone from an
      authoritative server, and can opportunistically refresh TTLs of
      previously cached records within the zone without making
      additional queries over the network to refresh expired
      records.</t>

    </abstract>

